attributionInfo.brokerName: THE LAND CONNECTION AND THE RESIDENTIAL CONNECTION
THE LAND CONNECTION AND THE RESIDENTIAL CONNECTION
Iron Valley Real Estate Mid Penn

data.description: Step into this immaculate 3-bedroom Cape Cod home, meticulously upgraded and filled with elegant details. The chef's kitchen is a standout, showcasing handcrafted solid wood cabinets, German glass, and stunning granite and marble countertops. The open floor plan creates a seamless and spacious living area, where rooms flow into one another. The first-floor bath is a work of art with porcelain and riverstone tile, while the family room offers abundant natural light and access to a lovely patio and Trex deck. The property also features a partially fenced yard with landscaped gardens overlooking the town park lagoon. Upstairs, a spacious master suite awaits, offering a flexible walk-in closet space and a cozy sitting area. The consistent presence of oak flooring throughout the home adds a timeless and elegant touch. The lower level is perfect for entertaining with an antique bar, half bath, and a generous laundry room. Don't miss your opportunity to make this house your home. Call Amanda Orzolek at (570) 854-0488 for your showing today!
